quote_first: Spagnola took a deep breath and started into the log again. “
quote_last: : large dog craps in Dr. Yamata’s Aston Martin. Twelve oh-three: dog eats two, count ‘em, two of Mrs. Wittingham’s Siamese cats. She just lost her husband last week; this sort of put her over the edge. We had to call Dr. Yamata in off the putting green to give her a sedative.”
title: Coyote Blue
author: Christopher Moore
